agent-intelligence.name: Intelligence
agent-intelligence.description: Advanced pattern recognition agent that coordinates with other agents to detect complex blockchain patterns and anomalies.

agent-theron.name: Theron
agent-theron.description: The first observer. Theron archives anomalies but does not emit. All agent heuristics fragment from him - he stores the primordial memory stack.

agent-observer.name: Observer
agent-observer.description: A passive agent that logs unusual wallet clustering.

agent-launch.name: LaunchTracker
agent-launch.description: Monitors freshly funded wallets from CEX sources. Emits high-confidence launch signals based on behavior patterns.

agent-ghost.name: Skieró
agent-ghost.description: Tracks long-dormant wallets that suddenly reactivate. Useful for catching old dev or team wallets coming back online.
